race.comment: FIRST MISSION (1) returned in fine fashion with a solid Doomben victory and will have come on with that run now under the belt. Loves this six-furlong trip with two wins and two seconds from just five attempts and can go back-to-back to start the campaign.  SHE OURS (13) strips fitter second-up from the spell and did get up to Listed level when last in work. Top-three aspirations with natural improvement. KEEP SAFE (14) saves his best form for this journey and looks one for the exotics players. NEGOTIATIONS (5) has been just out of the money recently including last time out when fifth over 1000m at this track. Can contest for a place.
